---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Notice | Call Brad" description="Privacy Notice - Call Brad GDPR Compliance Services">
  
  <!-- Privacy Notice Content -->
  <div class="pt-24 pb-14 lg:pt-32 lg:pb-18">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-montserrat text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-2">Privacy Notice</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Version 1.0</p>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Welcome to Call Brad. We are committed to protecting and respecting your privacy. This Privacy Notice explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our services.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">1. Data Controller</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Trauko OÜ (an Estonian company with registry code 16686838) is the data controller for the personal data you provide. You can contact us at <a href="mailto:javier@callbrad.eu" class="text-[#2b2e83] hover:underline">javier@callbrad.eu</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">2. Data Collection</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            The primary personal data we collect from you includes your name and email address. This information is requested when you set up a consultation with us via our Notion Calendar booking page or through email communication. Additionally, we may request other personal data as necessary for the provision of our services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">3. Purpose of Data Collection</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">We use your personal data exclusively for the following purposes:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Communicating about any appropriate business opportunities.</li>
            <li>Providing and improving our services.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">We process your personal data based on the following legal grounds:</p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Consent</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">By setting up a call with us via our Notion Calendar booking page or writing an email to us for the provision of services, you consent to the processing of your personal data (Article 6(1)(a) GDPR).</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Performance of a Contract</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Processing your data is necessary for the performance of a contract to which you are a party or in order to take steps at your request prior to entering into a contract (Article 6(1)(b) GDPR).</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We will retain your personal data only for as long as is necessary for the purposes set out in this Privacy Notice. Your data will be deleted when it is no longer required for these purposes or you withdraw your consent, subject to any legal obligations to retain the data.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">6. Your Rights Under the GDPR</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Under the GDPR, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Right to Access:</strong>
                <span class="text-gray-600">You have the right to request access to your personal data and obtain information on how we process it.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Right to Rectification:</strong>
                <span class="text-gray-600">You have the right to request correction of any inaccurate or incomplete personal data we hold about you.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Right to Erasure:</strong>
                <span class="text-gray-600">You have the right to request the deletion of your personal data, subject to certain conditions.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Right to Restriction of Processing:</strong>
                <span class="text-gray-600">You have the right to request the restriction of processing your personal data under certain circumstances.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Right to Data Portability:</strong>
                <span class="text-gray-600">You have the right to receive your personal data in a structured, commonly used, and machine-readable format and have the right to transmit those data to another controller.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Right to Object:</strong>
                <span class="text-gray-600">You have the right to object to the processing of your personal data under certain circumstances.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#ed60ed] rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-gray-800">Right to Withdraw Consent:</strong>
                <span class="text-gray-600">You have the right to withdraw your consent at any time. If you wish to withdraw your consent, please contact us at <a href="mailto:javier@callbrad.eu" class="text-[#2b2e83] hover:underline">javier@callbrad.eu</a>. Upon receiving your withdrawal request, we will cease processing your personal data and delete it from our records, unless we have a legitimate reason to retain it.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">7. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We take appropriate technical and organisational measures to ensure the security of your personal data and to protect it against unauthorised or unlawful processing and against accidental loss, destruction, or damage.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">8. Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Our website uses cookies of four types:</p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Essential Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">These cookies enable core functionality such as security, verification of identity, and network management. These cookies can't be disabled.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Marketing Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">These cookies are used to track advertising effectiveness to provide a more relevant service and deliver better ads to suit your interests.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Functional Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">These cookies collect data to remember choices users make to improve and give a more personalised experience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Analytics Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">These cookies help us to understand how visitors interact with our website, discover errors, and provide better overall analytics.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
            Only Essential cookies are mandatory. All other cookies are completely optional for you. This means that in order to use these cookies we need to gain your permission (consent) first.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">
            If you have any questions about the use of cookies on our website, please send an email to <a href="mailto:javier@callbrad.eu" class="text-[#2b2e83] hover:underline">javier@callbrad.eu</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">9. Changes to This Privacy Notice</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We may update this Privacy Notice from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Notice on our website. You are advised to review this Privacy Notice periodically for any changes.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Notice or our data protection practices, please contact us at <a href="mailto:javier@callbrad.eu" class="text-[#2b2e83] hover:underline">javier@callbrad.eu</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-[#2b2e83] font-medium hover:underline">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/>
          </svg>
          Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
